一.GraphLab的问题
1.内存占用大
    所需内存是原始数据的10倍以上，需要过多结点计算，引入了不必要的通信和并行开销
    50000篇文章训练50000个topic,model占用超过60G内存
    90000        40000                   60
    90782(413076词汇)        10000        20
    90782(413076词汇)        5000        10

    选择的频道:社会,科技,国际,体育,娱乐
二。数据入库
    建表:
    topic_models:
    news_topic:
    usertopics:    {'1':(权重,创建时间,失效时间1), '2':(权重,创建时间,失效时间)}

    用到的sql:
    "delete from usertopics where uid = '{0}' and model_v = '{1}' and ch_name='{2}' and topic_id='{3}'"
    "insert into usertopics (uid, model_v, ch_name, topic_id, probability, create_time, fail_time) VALUES ('{0}', '{1}', '{2}', '{3}', '{4}', '{5}', '{6}')"
    "update usertopics set probability='{0}', create_time='{1}', fail_time='{2}' where uid='{3}' and model_v='{4}' and ch_name='{5}' and topic_id='{6}'"
    "select uid, nid, max(ctime) ctime from newsrecommendclick  where CURRENT_DATE - INTEGER '3' <= DATE(ctime) group by uid,nid"
    'SELECT a.nid FROM newslist_v2 a RIGHT OUTER JOIN (select * from channellist_v2 where cname in ({0})) c ON a.chid=c.id ORDER BY nid DESC LIMIT {1}'


三。接口说明:
     1.对外提供的新闻nid入队列的接口
     url形式: http://120.55.88.11:9986/topic_model/predict_news_topic
     方法类型: GET方法
     参数说明: nid-----新闻id, int类型

